[SHORT DESC]
Type changes depending on the held plate. Prevents item loss.

[LONG DESC]
<p>This Pokemon changes its type on switching in depending on the plate heldâ€”each plate corresponds to a different type. This Pokemon is immune to all item removal effects: <a href="/dp/moves/covet">Covet</a>, <a href="/dp/moves/knock_off">Knock Off</a>, <a href="/dp/moves/switcheroo">Switcheroo</a>, <a href="/dp/moves/thief">Thief</a>, and <a href="/dp/moves/trick">Trick</a>. This ability can't be copied or stolen by <a href="/dp/abilities/role_play">Role Play</a>, <a href="/dp/abilities/skill_swap">Skill Swap</a>, or <a href="/dp/abilities/trace">Trace</a>. It cannot be suppressed by <a href="/dp/moves/gastro_acid">Gastro Acid</a> or <a href="/dp/moves/worry_seed">Worry Seed<a></p>